item.description:
Hi all,

Let's meetup and climb at Metrorock this Wednesday 28th November at 6:00pm. I can only climb till 8pm so I've scheduled this one to start earlier. However people are more then welcome to climb beyond 8pm!

I will be waiting around the picnic table till 6:15PM. Afterwards you can spot me wearing a plain red shirt and green pants.

On the night I'll post a message on the whiteboard between the men's and women's change rooms to let people know I'm there.

Cheers
Duc
item.name: Metrorock Wednesday, November 28 at 6:00 pm
